---
// src/components/SeoContent.astro
---
<section class="bg-white py-20 px-8">
  <div class="container mx-auto">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-4 text-gray-900" style="line-height: 1.5;">Your Challenges. Our Solutions.</h2>
      <p class="text-xl text-gray-600">From warped wood to workflow chaos, these climate-related problems blindside even the best-run projects. Unless you stop them at the gate.</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-12">
      <!-- Time Challenges -->
      <div class="text-center">
        <div class="bg-[#0955A9] rounded-full w-16 h-16 flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6">
          <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 6v6h4.5m4.5 0a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-gray-900" style="line-height: 1.4;">Time</h3>
        <div class="text-left space-y-3">
          <p class="text-gray-600">• Inconsistent site climate warps materials, driving up costs and blowing schedules.</p>
          <p class="text-gray-600">• Damage triggers rework that pushes every trade's timeline back.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Money Challenges -->
      <div class="text-center">
        <div class="bg-[#0955A9] rounded-full w-16 h-16 flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6">
          <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 6v12m-3-2.818l.879.659c1.171.879 3.07.879 4.242 0 1.172-.879 1.172-2.303 0-3.182C13.536 12.219 12.768 12 12 12c-.725 0-1.45-.22-2.003-.659-1.106-.879-1.106-2.303 0-3.182s2.9-.879 4.006 0l.415.33M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-gray-900" style="line-height: 1.4;">Money</h3>
        <div class="text-left space-y-3">
          <p class="text-gray-600">• Climate-controlled units keep materials pristine, cutting pricey replacements.</p>
          <p class="text-gray-600">• Mobile storage trims handling, warehousing, and damage expenses.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Logistics Challenges -->
      <div class="text-center">
        <div class="bg-[#0955A9] rounded-full w-16 h-16 flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6">
          <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M7.5 21L3 16.5m0 0L7.5 12M3 16.5h13.5m0-13.5L21 7.5m0 0L16.5 12M21 7.5H7.5" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-gray-900" style="line-height: 1.4;">Logistics</h3>
        <div class="text-left space-y-3">
          <p class="text-gray-600">• Gooseneck trailers drop right on site, freeing workspace for all trades.</p>
          <p class="text-gray-600">• No more costly shuttles from distant warehouses.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Features Section -->
    <div class="mt-20">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-4 text-gray-900" style="line-height: 1.5;">Complete Climate Protection Features</h2>
      </div>
      
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-8">
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="bg-gray-100 rounded-full w-16 h-16 flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4 hover:bg-gray-200 transition-colors duration-300">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-gray-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M3.75 13.5l10.5-11.25L12 10.5h8.25L9.75 21.75 12 13.5H3.75z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-2 text-gray-900" style="line-height: 1.4;">Precision Climate Control</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Commercial-grade HVAC + humidifier/de-humidifier lock temperature.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="bg-gray-100 rounded-full w-16 h-16 flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4 hover:bg-gray-200 transition-colors duration-300">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-gray-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M3.75 13.5l10.5-11.25L12 10.5h8.25L9.75 21.75 12 13.5H3.75z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-2 text-gray-900" style="line-height: 1.4;">Plug-&-Play Power</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">On-board generator with shore-power option means zero reliance on site utilities or half-wired temp poles.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="bg-gray-100 rounded-full w-16 h-16 flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4 hover:bg-gray-200 transition-colors duration-300">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-gray-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9 17.25v1.007a3 3 0 01-.879 2.122L7.5 21h9l-.621-.621A3 3 0 0115 18.257V17.25m6-12V15a2.25 2.25 0 01-2.25 2.25H5.25A2.25 2.25 0 013 15V5.25m18 0A2.25 2.25 0 0018.75 3H5.25A2.25 2.25 0 003 5.25m18 0V12a2.25 2.25 0 01-2.25 2.25H5.25A2.25 2.25 0 013 12V5.25" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-2 text-gray-900" style="line-height: 1.4;">Real-Time Monitoring Portal</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Live dashboards, text message/email alerts, and HD cameras let you babysit your cargo from your phone, 24/7 nationwide.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="bg-gray-100 rounded-full w-16 h-16 flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4 hover:bg-gray-200 transition-colors duration-300">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-gray-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M8.25 18.75a1.5 1.5 0 01-3 0m3 0a1.5 1.5 0 00-3 0m3 0h6m-9 0H3.375a1.125 1.125 0 01-1.125-1.125V14.25m6.75 4.5v-3a1.5 1.5 0 00-1.5-1.5m3 4.5v-3a1.5 1.5 0 011.5-1.5m-3 3h3m-3 0h-3m12 0h3.375c.621 0 1.125-.504 1.125-1.125V13.5m-3.75 5.25v-3a1.5 1.5 0 00-1.5-1.5M15 8.25h3.375c.621 0 1.125.504 1.125 1.125V13.5h-3.75v5.25" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-2 text-gray-900" style="line-height: 1.4;">Rapid Roll-In Deployment</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">We deliver, level, and dial-in climate in under 30 minutes; your crew can load materials the same morning.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

 